{
  "stem": "512.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the Russian soldiers came up on the train with a gun to her head and took that piece of bundle with nothing in it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Took it off her-- this is how-- that's how they-- they-- their mentality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were also-- the Russian soldiers were also on the verge of starvation, too, because they never had enough food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided we were going to meet in Budapest at a later date.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My community-- sheer horror.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolute horror.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The memories-- I thought I'm not going to be out there alive from the pain-- terrible, terrible pain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother, as I told you, was a very well-to-do widow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had one son.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was my uncle and he was in and out of the service also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had some gold, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She had some valuable things and she buried it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- I knew where it was buried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I thought I'll go there and see whether I'll find something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when I got to Bilky, they told me don't even bother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a Catholic school, surrounded with heavy, violent dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wouldn't let you close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I didn't even bother, because I knew it would've been terribly, terribly painful to go there, also, because she had like a huge estate.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But to go into the house where we lived with a hope that maybe there's going to be a photograph.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's about the only thing I was interested-- nothing else, because I didn't plan on staying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just wanted to see whether somebody did return and was looking for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's how you communicated.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
